All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, javax.servlet.ServletResponse
public class CharResponseWrapper
extends org.apache.slide.webdav.logger.StatusHttpServletResponseWrapper

CharResponseWrapper wrapps the response of a servlet for a filter Impromptu ProxyFilter uses it to find whether the resource is not available locally and should be fetched from a remote repository Most code is copied from other sources. This class should be part of the standard. This might not be used if we choose to filter the request instead of the response

Author:
Jie Ren
